name: CambioML
headline: Retrieve and transform data from PDFs and forms
description: CambioML providing ML tools for extracting and reconstruct text and data from PDFs, HTMLs and forms. Join the enterprise data gold mining from your legacy docs.

founders.name: Rachel Hu, Founder
founders.description: Co-founder and CEO of CambioML. Previously Applied Scientist at AWS; Built LLMs and Led open-source ML projects D2L.ai adopted by over 500 universities around the world; AWS senior speaker: talked at AWS re:Invent, Nvidia GTC, KDD, etc..

generated_description:
CambioML, a company founded in 2023 and part of the Y Combinator Batch S23, is shaking up the world of data extraction from documents with its innovative tool, AnyParser. Their mission is straightforward but powerful: to retrieve and transform data from PDF files and forms, enabling businesses to mine valuable insights from their legacy documents. If you've ever wrestled with cumbersome data extraction processes, you'll appreciate what CambioML offers.

At its core, CambioML started with machine learning-powered tools designed to accurately extract and reconstruct text and data from PDFs, HTML documents, and forms. With a small but focused team of three, the startup is poised to make a substantial impact. Their current offering, AnyParser, streamlines the document parsing process, allowing users to drag and drop various document types—PDFs, PPTs, Word files, and images—and pull out structured data in a mere few clicks.

What makes AnyParser stand out? Well, it doesn’t just grab text; it handles complex layouts, including tables, charts, and footnotes, with unmatched precision. Unlike many traditional OCR tools that often require tedious post-processing, AnyParser achieves up to 2.5 times more recall and 2 times more precision compared to industry averages. It incorporates privacy features that automatically redact personally identifiable information during extraction, making it suitable for businesses that prioritize data security.

Users of AnyParser have praised it for its ease of use, speed, and remarkable accuracy. Jobright, a prominent job search platform, reported that AnyParser outperformed more than ten other parsers, establishing itself as the fastest and most reliable solution available.

The company is led by some savvy leadership, including their Group Partner Michael Seibel, who has a proven track record in helping startups thrive. With a clean and functional website [CambioML.com](https://www.cambioml.com/), they're making it easy for businesses to access their API and try out their sandbox for free—no credit card needed!

In summary, CambioML is on a mission to transform legacy documents into actionable data with their advanced parsing technology. For anyone dealing with large volumes of unstructured data, it’s a game-changer ready to simplify extraction processes and drive productivity. Keep an eye on this promising startup—they're just getting started!
